00:09:10.799 --> 00:09:16.719
assessed this package. I think it will or will not be a good candidate for our GXP environment

00:09:17.359 --> 00:09:22.239
to do, you know, whatever intended analysis that you're seeking to do.

00:09:22.239 --> 00:09:27.119
And I feel like communicating with quality teams and QA is such an important initiative

00:09:27.119 --> 00:09:31.200
and getting information to them about these packages and tools is a

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:33.520
really awesome thing that your team is working on.

00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:34.400
